      "body": "```html\n<html>\n  <head>\n  %@LW_pgstart@@\n    <title>Invoice</title>\n    <style>\n      body {\n        background-color: #fff;\n        font-family: sans-serif;\n        padding-left: 40px;\n        padding-top: 70px;\n        padding-right: 30px;\n        padding-bottom: 20px;\n        width:840px;\n        height:850px;\n      }\n      th{\n        background-color:#337ab7;\n        color:000;\n        height: 10px;\n      }\n      .isi tr:nth-child(even){\n        background-color : #d4d0ff;\n      }\n      .customers tr:hover{\n        background-color : #ddd;\n      }\n\n      table {\n        border-collapse:collapse;\n      }\n      hr{\n        \tdisplay: block;\n    \t\theight: 1px;\n    \t\tbackground: transparent;\n    \t\twidth: 100%;\n    \t\tborder: none;\n    \t\tborder-top: solid 0.1px #000;\n            margin-top: 0px;\n            margin-bottom: 0px;\n        }\n\n      .isi table, .isi td, .isi th {\n        border:1px solid black; \n      }\n      #head  table, #head td, #head th{\n        border:none !important; \n      }\n      @media print {    \n        .no-print, .no-print *\n        {\n          display: none !important;\n        }\n      }\n\n    </style>\n    <style>\n      .text1{\n        font-size: 11px;\n      }\n      .text2{\n        font-size: 14px;\n      }\n    </style>\n  </head>\n  <body text=\"#000\" style=\"background-color:%LW_color_bg%\">\n\n    LW_pgstart@%\n\n    %@LW_prowno_0@@\n    <button class=\"no-print\" onclick=\"window.print()\">Print</button>\n    <table width=\"100%\">\n      <tr>\n      \t<td width=\"80px\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"../..//company/logo.jpg\" width=\"70px\" height=\"70px\"></td>\n        <td colspan=\"8\" style=\"font-size:20px\">%@LW_PField_Pub_company@%</td>\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"7\" style=\"font-size:16px\">%@LW_PField_Pub_adr1@%</td>\n      </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30px\" valign=\"top\">\n      \t<td colspan=\"12\" style=\"font-size:20px\" align=\"center\">INVOICE</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td></td>\n      \t<td></td>\n    \t<td>Nomor</td>\n    \t<td>:</td>\n    \t<td>%@LW_PField_fa_nofak@%</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td></td>\n      \t<td></td>\n    \t<td>Tanggal</td>\n    \t<td>:</td>\n    \t<td>%@LW_PField_DtoStr(fa_dtfak,DD/MM/YY)@%</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n    \t<td align=\"right\">Yth :</td>\n    \t<td>%@LW_PField_fa_Name@%</td>\n    \t<td width=\"30px\"></td>\n    \t<td>No. PO</td>\n    \t<td>:</td>\n    \t<td>%@LW_PField_fa_noorder@%</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td width=\"450px\" rowspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_adr1+fa_adr2+fa_adr3@%</td>\n    \t<td width=\"30px\"></td>\n    \t<td>No. SJ</td>\n    \t<td>:</td>\n    \t<td>%@LW_PField_fa_origin@%</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30px\" valign=\"top\">\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td></td>\n    \t<td width=\"100px\" valign=\"top\">Description</td>\n    \t<td valign=\"top\">:</td>\n    \t<td rowspan=\"2\">%@LW_PField_fa_descr@%</td>\n    </tr>\n    </table>\n  <table width=\"100%\">\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"12\"><hr align=\"left\" style=\"border: 0.1px solid; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px\"></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td width=\"30px\">No.</td>\n        <td style=\"padding-right:5px\">No. PO</td>\n        <td width=\"100px\">Kode</td>\n        <td colspan=\"3\">Keterangan</td>\n        <td align=\"right\">Qty</td>\n        <td style=\"padding-left:10px\">Unit</td>\n        <td align=\"right\">Unit Price</td>\n        <td align=\"right\">%Disc</td>\n        <td align=\"right\">Amount</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"12\"><hr align=\"left\" style=\"border: 0.1px solid; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px\"></td>\n      </tr>\n      LW_prowno_0@%\n    \n       %@LW_prowno_10@@\n          <tr height=\"25px\">%@LW_PRow_add@1@%\n            <td width=\"30px\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField__drow@%</td>\n            <td style=\"padding-right:5px\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_noorder@%</td>\n            <td width=\"100px\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_itemId@%</td>\n            <td width=\"200px\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_descr@%</td>\n            <td valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_descr2@%</td>\n            <td valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_descr3@%</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_qty@N6/0,N@%</td>\n            <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-left:10px\">%@LW_PField_fa_unit@%</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_hgsat@N6/0,N@%</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_qdis+fa_qdis2@N6/0,N@%</td>\n            <td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\">%@LW_PField_fa_hrg-fa_hpot-fa_hpot2@N9/0,N,8,1@%</td>\n          </tr>\n       LW_prowno_10@%\n  \t\t</table>\n      \n      %@LW_prowno_209@@\n  \t\t<table width=\"100%\">\n          <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"12\"><hr align=\"left\" style=\"border: 0.1px solid; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px\"></td>\n          </tr>\n       LW_prowno_209@%\n      \n      %@LW_prowno_299@@\n          <tr height=\"20px\">\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td align=\"right\">Sub Total :</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:right\">%@LW_PField_fa_hrg@N16/0,N@%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr height=\"20px\">\n            <td></td>\n            <td></td>\n            <td align=\"right\">PPN :</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:right\">%@LW_PField_fa_htax@N16/0,N@%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr height=\"30px\">\n            <td>Terbilang :</td>\n            <td>%@LW_PField_bilang(fa_harga)@%</td>\n            <td align=\"right\">TOTAL :</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:right\">%@LW_PField_fa_harga@N16/0,N@%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"12\"><hr align=\"left\" style=\"border: 0.1px solid; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px\"></td>\n          </tr>\n    </table>\n    <table width=\"100%\">\n          <tr height=\"50px\" align=\"center\">\n            <td width=\"250px\">Prepare By</td>\n            <td width=\"250px\">Received By</td>\n            <td width=\"250px\">Approved By</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr height=\"100px\" align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\">\n            <td width=\"250px\">_____________________</td>\n            <td width=\"250px\">_____________________</td>\n            <td width=\"250px\">_____________________</td>\n          </tr>\n       LW_prowno_299@%\n    </table>\n  </body>\n%@LW_pgend@@\nLW_pgend@%\n</html>\n```\n\n**AP520**\n\nReport AP520 menampilkan invoice Payable, dapat berupa invoice pembelian, invoice beli hutang, dll.\n\n**Penjelasan HTM**\n\n`%@LW_PField__drow@%`\n\n**_drow** merupakan variabel yang menampilkan nomor row sesuai pengulangan pada **ProwNo**. Pada report HTM ini digunakan untuk menampilkan nomor baris item pada report di Prowno 10.\n\n`%@LW_PField_bilang(fa_harga)@%`\n\n**bilang()** menampilkan jumlah angka pada field **fa_harga** menjadi terbilang.\n\nPada report HTM ini digunakan untuk membuat terbilang **total** pada invoice\n\nJika fa_harga bernilai 23500 maka output fungsi diatas adalah \"dua puluh tiga ribu lima ratus\"\n\n`%@LW_PField_DtoStr(fa_dtfak,DD/MM/YY)@%`\n\n**DtoStr()** berfungsi mengubah format tanggal sesuai dengan keperluan format tanggal pada laporan.\n\nPada report HTM ini untuk menampilkan tanggal invoice dengan format dd/mm/yy\n\nJika fa_dtfak bernilai 20201231 maka output fungsi diatas adalah \"31/12/20\"\\\n\\\n\\\nhttps://larona.id/manual/Report/contoh_report/AP520_output.html"
